scrot for Debian
----------------

To use scrot with cron, you need to set the DISPLAY variable. See the following
example:

    DISPLAY=:0 scrot -z -q 20 -e 'mv $f /var/backups/scrot/'

To discover the current DISPLAY, use this command:

    $ echo $DISPLAY

